    nodejs
Description: VS Code extension for JS eval and Chrome CDP input injection
 vscode-devtools provides two developer tools for VS Code:
 .
  - Eval Selection: executes selected JavaScript and appends output inline.
  - Input Inject Panel: sends key sequences to a Chrome tab via CDP.
 .
 This package builds extension artifacts from TypeScript sources.
